JOLLY LLB 3

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Thangapoovey - Video Song | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil presents the video song of “Thangapoovey” from the much-awaited film Madharaasi, written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh’s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film’s emotional landscape.

snippet.title: The Chase Teaser: R Madhavan & MS Dhoni Together | Mahi in Action Avatar | Vasan Bala
snippet.description:
The Chase Teaser: R Madhavan & MS Dhoni Together | Mahi in Action Avatar | Vasan Bala


Friends the wait is finally over! On 7th September, R. Madhavan dropped a massive surprise on social media – the official teaser of “The Chase” directed by Vasan Bala. But the real shocker? Legendary cricketer MS Dhoni joins Madhavan as a Task Force Officer! Both Madhavan and Dhoni are seen in uniform, bringing raw action and power-packed energy on screen. The teaser has already gone viral on Instagram and fans can’t stop saying – “Maddy and Mahi together = Fire!” Dhoni, who has earlier appeared in ads and even a cameo in Tamil movie “GOAT,” is now seen in a completely new avatar that has left fans speechless. Meanwhile, Madhavan continues to surprise audiences with versatile roles, and this time he looks deadlier than ever!

snippet.title: Soniya Soniya Telugu Lyrical Song | Rakshakudu | Nagarjuna, Sushmita Sen | A.R. Rahman |Udit Narayan
snippet.description:
Listen & Enjoy the Melodious Soniya Soniya Telugu Lyrical Song from Rakshakudu Movie. Featuring Nagarjuna & Sushmita Sen, with Music by A.R. Rahman. Sung by Udit Narayan, P. Unnikrishnan & Harini, Lyrics by Bhuvanachandra, and Directed by Praveen Gandhi.

Song Details:
Song Name: Soniya Soniya
Singers: P. Unnikrishnan, Udit Narayan, Harini
Lyrics: Bhuvanachandra
Music Director: A.R. Rahman

Movie Details:
Movie Name: Rakshakudu
Banner: J.R.S. Combines
Producer: J. Rama Chandra Rao
Director: Praveen Gandhi
Audio On: Aditya Music.

Soniya Soniya Song Telugu Lyrics:

సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా సోనియా ఆఆ
సోనియా సోనియా స్వీటు స్వీటు సోనియా రేగుతోంది లేత వయసు జోరు  
ఘాటు లవ్వు  రెండు టైపు నీటుదొకటి  నాటుదొకటి
రెండిట్లో ఏది నీకు ప్యారు
Sometimes  నీటే స్వీటు… Sometimes నాటే రైటు…
పిల్ల కళ్ళని చూసీ చేసేయ్ గురువా ఫైటు   || సోనియా|| 2
పువ్వుల్ని తడిమే చిరుగాలి మల్లె చెక్కిళ్ళు తడితే అది నీటు
కొమ్మల్ని విరిచే సుడిగాలి మల్లె ఒడి చేర్చుకుంటే అది నాటు
పచ్చిక మీద పడే చినుకుల మల్లె చిరు ముద్దులు పెట్టి శృతి చేయడమే నీటు
కసిగా మీద పడే ఉప్పన్నమల్లే చెలి పైటని పట్టి చిత్తు చేయడమే నాటు
నీ కురుల మీద పువ్వుని నేనై మురిపించే ఆట ఆడించనా
మృదువైన ముద్దుల్లో సొగసే ఉందే మంచంలో మాటలకి చోటేముందే
మత్తెక్కి కౌగిట్లో ముంచేస్తా అమ్మడు || సోనియా||
 
ఊరించే ఒడిలో  ఉపొంగే తడిలో బుగల్ని ఎంచక్కా పిండేస్తుంటే
పరువాల పిలుపే కళ్ళలో మెరుపై గుండెల్లో సెగలే రగిలిస్తుంటే
కౌగిలి క్రికెట్కి సిస్టమ్ లేదే అంపైరు లేడే మగతనముంటే చాలే
పట్టి పడతోస్తే వేగేదెట్టా బరువాపేదెట్టా ఎద మల్లెలపూవానోయ్
నలిపైకపోతే అందం లేదే కసి లేని మొహం మొహం కాదే
కోమలితో వాదిస్తే అర్ధం ఉందా కవ్వించి కాటేస్తే న్యాయం ఉందా
ప్రేయసిని గెలిచేది నా చూపుతానమేగా 
||సోనియా||

#jaani  #filhall #akshaykumar #bpraak  
Have you ever selflessly loved someone so much that just their smile can brighten up your day? 

FILHALL, a feel good song about love and it’s beauty of never giving up. 

From the makers of iconic songs like Qismat , Maan Bhariya , Pachtaoge  and Coka , one of bollywood most celebrated Artist Akshay Kumar  Featuring Nupur sanon , bring to you, their first ever debut Music video , in the voice of Bpraak . The video , shot is done by the concept king Arvindr Khaira  and penned down by one and only lyrical machine JAANI . Filhaal, a song that depicts the story of that true love which is pious, selfless yet incomplete. 

Desi Melodies proudly presents FILHALL  In association with cape of Good films & Azeem Dayani

Lyrics:
Orupodhum visuvasathai vittuvidaadheergal
(Never let go of the faith)
Neengal visuvasithaal ellam koodumae 
(If you believe, everything will be possible)

Kadugalavu visuvasam irundhale podhum
(If you have mustard-seed sized faith,)
Yengugindra kaariyangal ellamae aagum
(Whatever you long for will happen)

Siricha mugamai varuvaaru
(With a smiling face, He will come)
Sirandhadhai ellamai tharuvaaru
(He will give you the best of everything)

1. Yobuvin vaazhkaiyai pola 
(Like the life of Job,)
Pala vidha (pala pala) kashtangal soola 
(In the midst of many kinds of trouble,)
Soraamal kartharai nee pidithukondal
(If you hold on to the Lord without growing weary,)

Yobuvin aasirvadham unaku undu 
(Job’s blessing belongs to you)
Ilanthadhai irandu madangaai petrukondu
(You will get back whatever you have lost in double measure)
Ini sezhipaaga nee vazhndhidu
(From now on, you will live prosperously)

2. Kulandhaiyin selvathirkaaga 
(For the gift of child,)
Yaengidum saaraalaaga 
(Longing like Sarah,)
Pala naatkal kaathirundhu azhugindraaiyo
(Have you been tearfully waiting many days?)

Abraghamin aasirvadham unaku undu 
(Abraham’s blessing belongs to you)
Naalaanaalum nichaiyamaaga mudivu undu 
(Even though it takes time, surely there is an end)
Un nambikkai veen pogaadhu
(Your hope will not be cut off)

℗ 2025 Stella Ramola

#StellaRamola #DanielDavidson #TamilChristianSong #SteDan #Visuvasam #MustardSeedFaith #NewTamilChristianSong #TamilChristianSong2025 #SteDansMusicRoom

snippet.title: Franklin & Shinchan Celebrate Onam with Maveli 🏆 Mammootty & Mohanlal in GTA 5 Malayalam
snippet.description:
✨ Happy Onam to everyone! 🌼
In this Onam Special GTA 5 Malayalam video, Franklin, Shinchan, and friends celebrate Onam with Mahabali, Mammootty, and Mohanlal. From Onasadya feasts to Onam games like KSRTC bus race, food eating challenge, and boat race, the fun never stops! 🎉

👉 Watch Franklin & Shinchan’s team win the Onam challenges and receive a grand gift of 10 villas from Mahabali before he returns to Paatalam. This Onam is full of laughter, challenges, and family celebrations.

🔥 Don’t miss this festive episode packed with comedy, action, and surprises!

#OnamSpecial #GTA5Malayalam #FranklinAndShinchan #Mammootty #Mohanlal #Mahabali

snippet.title: वीरवार स्पेशल  | Vishnu Ji Ke Bhajan | विष्णु जी के भजन |Ekadashi Bhajan | Hari Ke Bhajan | Bhajan
snippet.description:
वीरवार स्पेशल  | Vishnu Ji Ke Bhajan | विष्णु जी के भजन |Ekadashi Bhajan | Hari Ke Bhajan | Bhajan

तो आईए आज पावन हृदय से इस भजन द्वारा जो मांगना है मांग लीजिए।
श्याम बाबा सबकी मनोकामनांए पूर्ण करें। 🙏

⭐Bhajan : 
रचा है सृष्टि को जिस प्रभु ने
श्री मन नारायण नारायण हरि 
मेरा छोटा सा परिवार हरि 
हरि नाम न ह्रदय से भूलों
हर सांस मे हो सुमिरन तेरा
श्री विष्णु अमृतवाणी
भगवान मेरी नैया उस पार लगा 
श्री  विष्णु जी के 108 नाम
ॐ नमो भगवते वासुदेवाय 
सत्यनारायण जी की आरती

⭐Singer : Upasana Mehta & Sanchit 
⭐Lyrics :  Archana Agarwa & Sachin Tulsiyan &Traditional
⭐Music: Binny Narang (9991980610)
⭐Video: Shalini Sharma (7015960610)
⭐Label Bhakti Sadhna (9466651081)
⭐Category: Hindi Devotional (Shyam Bhajan)
 
भक्ति साधना कंपनी  संपर्क करे 9466651081

सिमरु मै शिव का नाम,
अब तो दुनियादारी से है,
मेरा क्या काम....

शिव के रंग में ऐसी डूबा,
बन गया एक ही रूप,
शिव की माला जपते जपते,
हो गयी सुबह श्याम,
सांसो की माला पे.....

शिवजी मेरे दिल में बसे है,
संग रहे दिन रात,
अपने मन की मै जानू ,
सब के मन की राम,
सांसो की माला पे....

शिवजी मेरे अंतरयामी,
शिवजी मेरे स्वामी,
शिवजी के चरणों में अर्पण,
ये जीवन तमाम,
सांसो की माला पे....

प्रेम पियाला जबसे पिया है,
जी का है ये हाल,
अंगारों पे नींद आ जाए,
और कांटो पे आराम,
सांसो की माला पे....

सांसो की माला पे,
सिमरु मै शिव का नाम,
अब तो दुनियादारी से है,
मेरा क्या काम,
सांसो की माला पे,
सिमरु मै शिव का नाम.....

snippet.description:
Presenting the Lyrical Video of #PuppyShame song from #AndhraKingTaluka

The energy, passion and fun of a fan in the voice of ‘Energetic Star’ Ram Pothineni. Music is by Vivek & Mervin. Lyrics by Bhaskarabhatla. Andhra King Taluka - A BIOPIC OF A FAN is a Telugu Film written and directed by Mahesh Babu P and produced by Naveen Yerneni, Y. Ravi Shankar under Mythri Movie Makers. 

The film brings untold emotions between a fan and a superstar onto the big screens on 28th November worldwide

snippet.title: Phool Maangu Na Bahaar Maangu | Udit Narayan | Madhuri Dixit, Sanjay Kapoor | 90s Romantic Song
snippet.description:
Enjoy the 90s romantic hit "Phool Maangu Na Bahaar Maangu" sung by Udit Narayan, featuring Madhuri Dixit and Sanjay Kapoor in this classic Bollywood song.

Phool Maangu Na Bahaar Maangu | Udit Narayan | Madhuri Dixit, Sanjay Kapoor | 90s Romantic Song

Movie: Raja (1995)
Song: Phool Maangu Na Bahaar Maangu
Starcast: Madhuri Dixit, Sanjay Kapoor
Singer: Udit Narayan, Alka Yagnik
Music Director: Nadeem Saifee, Shravan Kumar
Lyricist: Sameer

#90sromanticsongs #uditnarayan #alkayagnik #madhuridixit #sanjaykapoor #lovesong #hindigane #hindisongs #hindilovesongs #bollywoodsongs #bollywoodlovesongs #uditnarayansongs #uditnarayanhitssong #alkayagniksong #madhuridixitsong  

Song Lyrics :
Phool mangu na bahar mangu
Phool mangu na bahar mangu main to sanam tera pyar mangu
chain mangu na karar mangu
chain mangu na karar mangu main to sanam tera pyar mangu
phul mangu na bahar mangu

jo bhi chhupaya tha is dil me maine tujhko bataya
raze mohabbat maine bhi tujhse kabhi na chhupaya
kaisi hoti hai lagi mujhko to bata
isme hai bchainiya isme hai nasha
hosh mangu na khumar mangu
hosh mangu na khumar mangu main to sanam tera pyar mangu
phool mangu na bahar mangu
chain mangu na karar mangu main to sanam tera pyar mangu
phul mangu na bahar mangu

har dam chahe itna mujhe hoga na aisa diwana
tere liye main janejaha chhod u sara jamana
gujaregi kaise bhala tanha jidagi
ab to tere naam hai meri har khushi
rup mangu na singar mangu
rup mangu na singar mangu main to sanam tera pyar mangu
phool mangu na bahar mangu
chain mangu na karar mangu main to sanam tera pyar mangu

snippet.title: FIDE Grand Swiss 2025 | Round 7 | ft. Arjun, Nihal, Vaishali, Pragg, Gukesh, Vidit, Divya
snippet.description:
Chessneurons premium Membership for free for 1 months: https://forms.gle/5Toqah59yosCeM6BA

Check out the LIVESTREAM of FIDE: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PKSz0nAOLz4

Some of our Best selling products:
1. ChessBase 18 + Mega Database 2025: https://shop.chessbase.in/products/chessbase-18-mega-database-2025-combo
2. ChessBase India Premium Chess Set: https://shop.chessbase.in/products/chessbase-india-premium-chess-set
3. ChessPa meets Guki: https://shop.chessbase.in/products/chesspa-meets-guki-the-golden-boy-life-story-of-world-chess-champion-gukesh
4. The all new Fritz 20: https://shop.chessbase.in/products/fritz-20

The FIDE Grand Swiss and FIDE Women’s Grand Swiss 2025 will take place in Samarkand, Uzbekistan, from September 2 to 16, 2025.

Both tournaments are part of the qualifications for the World Championship cycle, with the top two players in the open event qualifying for the 2026 Candidates Tournament and the top two players in the Women’s Grand Swiss qualifying for the 2026 Women’s Candidates.
Eleven rounds will be played under the Swiss System, with 172 players participating from all continents: 116 in the Grand Swiss and 56 players in the Women’s Grand Swiss.

The total prize fund is $855,000, with $625,000 for the Grand Swiss and $230,000 for the Women’s Grand Swiss.

Held every two years, the Grand Swiss brings together many of the strongest chess players in the world and is considered to be one of the most difficult chess tournaments to win. The first Grand Swiss was held in 2019 in the Isle of Man and was won by GM Wang Hao, who scored 8/11. The 2021 edition was moved from the Isle of Man to Riga due to Covid restrictions on the island and was won by GM Alireza Firouzja in the Open and Lei Tingjie in the inaugural Women’s event. The 2023 Grand Swiss was won by India’s Vidit Gujrathi in the Open and Vaishali Rameshbabu in the Women’s competition.
